        "name": "Cymelle Technologies API v2",
        "description": "Comprehensive Postman collection for the Cymelle Multi-Service Backend.\n\n### Authentication\n- Register via `/api/v1/auth/register` (Roles: `ADMIN`, `CUSTOMER`, `DRIVER`)\n- Authenticate via `/api/v1/auth/authenticate` to get a JWT token.\n- Use the result token in the **Bearer Token** authorization of other requests.\n\n### Error Handling\nThe API returns standardized error responses:\n- `400 Bad Request`: Validation failures or logic errors (like Insufficient Stock).\n- `401 Unauthorized`: Bad credentials.\n- `403 Forbidden`: Insufficient permissions (e.g., Customer accessing Admin endpoints).\n- `404 Not Found`: Resource ID does not exist.\n- `409 Conflict`: Database integrity violation (e.g., deleting a product that has orders).",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
